- Everybody, come on!

41:13.889 --> 41:15.640
Man your defensive positions!

41:17.392 --> 41:18.393
Fire!

41:18.935 --> 41:20.187
Hey!

41:20.520 --> 41:21.855
Hey, let me fight!

